apierror-kartographer-conflicting-revids:
{{doc-apierror}}
Error message when attempting to use the mapdata query API with multiple revision IDs that belong to the same page.
kartographer-attribution: Attribution text shown at the bottom of the map.
kartographer-attribution-externaldata:
{{optional}}
Formats external data layer attribution:

Parameters:
* $1 - external data service (e.g. Wikidata)
* $2 - link to external data link (e.g. query).
kartographer-attribution-short:
{{optional}}
Shorter version of the attribution text shown at the bottom of the map, for static maps embedded in the article.
kartographer-broken-category:
{{tracking category name}}
Name of the tracking category
kartographer-broken-category-desc: Description on [[Special:TrackingCategories]] for the {{msg-mw|kartographer-broken-category}} tracking category.
kartographer-error-context:
{{Optional}}
General message shown before a single specific error

Parameters:
* $1 - tag name, 'mapframe' or 'maplink'
* $2 - error message
kartographer-error-context-multi:
General message shown before multiple errors

Parameters:
* $1 - tag name, 'mapframe', 'maplink' or 'mapdata'
* $2 - list of errors combined into a bullet list
kartographer-error-json:
Error message preceding general JSON syntax errors.

Parameters:
* $1 - underlying message from JSON parser
kartographer-error-json-schema-error:
List entry in a list of JSON schema validation errors.
Parameters: $1 - location of the error in the JSON
* $2 - message explaining the error
kartographer-error-missing-attr:
Error shown instead of a map when required parameter(s) is missing.

Parameters:
* $1 - non-localized attribute name, such as 'height', 'latitude', etc
kartographer-error-bad_attr:
Error shown instead of a map in case of a problem with parameters.

Parameters:
* $1 - non-localized attribute name, such as 'height', 'latitude', etc
kartographer-error-bad_data: This error is shown if the content of the tag is syntactically valid JSON however it does not adhere to GeoJSON and simplestyle specifications.
kartographer-error-latlon: {{doc-important|Do not translate latitude and longitude.}} Error shown by <maplink> or <mapframe> when certain parameters are incorrect
kartographer-error-title:
Error shown by <maplink> or <mapframe>.

Parameters:
* $1 - page title
kartographer-tracking-category:
{{tracking category name}}
Name of the tracking category
kartographer-tracking-category-desc: Description on [[Special:TrackingCategories]] for the {{msg-mw|kartographer-tracking-category}} tracking category.
kartographer-coord-combined:
{{optional}}
Joins two parts of geogrpahical coordinates.

Parameters:
* $1 - latitude
* $2 - longitude
kartographer-coord-dms:
{{optional}}
Formats geographical latitude or longitude into degrees, minutes and seconds.

Parameters:
* $1 - degrees
* $2 - minutes
* $3 - seconds
kartographer-specialmap-invalid-coordina: Displayed by Special:Map when no valid coordinates are supplied
